  "texts": [
    "First, they are clearly artifacts.",
    "Second, we create them to alter, modulate and control our emotivity.",
    "Recall: Replika is \"the AI companion who cares\".",
    "It is there with the purpose of looking after us and our emotive needs.",
    "And so, mutatis mutandis, is to a large extent Pepper."
